2026-02-26T03:53:14Z | 7ee5cc83117195808a81338d911e9fe68e87bc78 | Add admin impersonation page

Implements a new AdminImpersonate page that provides:
- Viewport-based impersonation preview (desktop/tablet/mobile) via an iframe
- Plan-based role selector with admin override, persisted in sessionStorage
- Navigation controls to preview arbitrary routes inside the iframe
- Route and UI updates to expose the impersonation page at /admin/impersonate
- Sidebar integration adding an Impersonar item in the Sistema group
- Admin dashboard routing updated to accommodate the new impersonation flow (and imports)

